ABOUT THE BOOK
Entrepreneurship ensures the creation of new ideas with newer, most effective methods to be
used in business. Truthfully, in pursuit of success as an entrepreneur, a person must use
innovation to improve the standards of goods and services.
This book will help readers acquire skills, knowledge, patience and mastery in related business
activities if they practise what they read in this piece. It will provide value, opportunity and
consistency to demonstrate the highest excellence in entrepreneurship. As an entrepreneur, you
should understand that risk, resources, capital and capacity building are essential for the
existence of an organization. Capacity building means the ability of the individual to continue to
improve the knowledge, skills, tools, and other resources needed to produce efficiency and
effectiveness. A proper understanding of skills, gifts and resources will help you create a strong
foundation for your future growth.
It is important to realise that entrepreneurship is not you, but it is about building a team to build a
strong network and thus achieve the desired results. With this perspective of networking and
accountability in mind, entrepreneurs will understand the value of time and thus work hard to
succeed. Success comes to every entrepreneur who willingly decides to make a profit to develop
business and solve people’s problems.
